author: vmassol
msg: Added new java property "cactus.config" to specify location of cactus properties file (you pass it on the command line, ex: "java -Dcactus.property=conf/mycactus.properties"). If not specified, Cactus will look for a "cactus.properties" file in the classpath.

author: vmassol
msg: removed explicit logging of entries and exits of methods (using aspectj now) + added new test "service" (we alreayd had "execute test" and "get result" services) which is simply used to verify if connection with the redirector is working and does nothing
